  "detailed_description": "<i><strong>Take back what they stole from you.</strong></i><br><br>You are part of the temporary testing team for project BEYOND and have been provided with a machine that can hack into any device in the world. You are asked to hack into devices and gather information to test the capabilities of this machine.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/56247351f4874351549203fe54f47d8c.avif?t=1705704543\" width=600 height=94 /></span><br>TERMINAL22 is a mix of bullet hell and puzzle gameplay, utilizing the aesthetic of an old operating system terminal. Hack into any system you can find, dig around in the files and uncover the secrets about your identity, the testing program, project BEYOND and the company behind it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/3cdc4452673ebc88bf4d47f9a56b4ec4.poster.avif?t=1705704543\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/3cdc4452673ebc88bf4d47f9a56b4ec4.webm?t=1705704543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/3cdc4452673ebc88bf4d47f9a56b4ec4.mp4?t=1705704543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>...before long you may realize that you might not be the only one looking into this.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/cc19e402637e22023812565337263208.avif?t=1705704543\" width=600 height=94 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/aa2b5ceaac0e23eb5636e111c2533d8b.webp?t=1705704543\" width=96 height=16 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>One of the two main elements of gameplay is hacking. Through the game you will need to hack into many different devices. This is done through a navigating your way through a bullet hell arena and finding all of the \"Security Nodes\" in order to break the security of the machine and access it.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/e667d187cf3b6ef3c446cc2675bf6fcd.poster.avif?t=1705704543\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/e667d187cf3b6ef3c446cc2675bf6fcd.webm?t=1705704543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/e667d187cf3b6ef3c446cc2675bf6fcd.mp4?t=1705704543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/1457a05e1354b858a5b1ed959ac406e5.webp?t=1705704543\" width=120 height=16 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Once getting into the machines, you will partake in the second major part of the gameplay, the discovery. Dig through the system by using terminal commands, discover files, go through them to learn the necessary information to progress further in the game.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/4047e470871b715b48faa9aede3156d3.poster.avif?t=1705704543\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/4047e470871b715b48faa9aede3156d3.webm?t=1705704543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/4047e470871b715b48faa9aede3156d3.mp4?t=1705704543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<i><strong>Take back what they stole from you.</strong></i><br><br>You are part of the temporary testing team for project BEYOND and have been provided with a machine that can hack into any device in the world. You are asked to hack into devices and gather information to test the capabilities of this machine.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/56247351f4874351549203fe54f47d8c.avif?t=1705704543\" width=600 height=94 /></span><br>TERMINAL22 is a mix of bullet hell and puzzle gameplay, utilizing the aesthetic of an old operating system terminal. Hack into any system you can find, dig around in the files and uncover the secrets about your identity, the testing program, project BEYOND and the company behind it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/3cdc4452673ebc88bf4d47f9a56b4ec4.poster.avif?t=1705704543\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/3cdc4452673ebc88bf4d47f9a56b4ec4.webm?t=1705704543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/3cdc4452673ebc88bf4d47f9a56b4ec4.mp4?t=1705704543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>...before long you may realize that you might not be the only one looking into this.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/cc19e402637e22023812565337263208.avif?t=1705704543\" width=600 height=94 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704020/extras/aa2b5ceaac0e23eb5636e111c2533d8b.webp?t=1705704543\" widt